property.name: description
property.value: Test top-level functions provided by the host.

property.name: getResource (port)
property.value: Outputs the contents of index.html if the host implements this.getResource() and can serve contents given 'index.html' as the URI.

property.name: httpRequest (port)
property.value: Outputs the contents of index.html if the host implements httpRequest() and can serve contents given 'index.html' as the URL.

property.name: readURL (port)
property.value: Outputs the contents of index.html if the host implements readURL() and can serve contents given 'index.html' as the URL.
